{"tid":2399508,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"泛民派揮春為612基金籌款","createTime":"2021-02-08T08:03:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-08T08:23:57.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2ba18126a2fae569b586479c725d60a0800b52e0","tid":2399508,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T08:03:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210208/VJNJDTZUFJF6RBJLT3SMQ4KGY4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210208%2FVJNJDTZUFJF6RBJLT3SMQ4KGY4%2F&d=wuzGI5SyrIdJ%2FUQuqXTUiqxOsK%2BJamotDVaNSe1I1zI%3D&h=9ddf25b5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210208%2FVJNJDTZUFJF6RBJLT3SMQ4KGY4%2F&h=7c664f7f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210208/VJNJDTZUFJF6RBJLT3SMQ4KGY4/</a><br />\n<br />\n泛民派揮春為612基金籌款<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/bZ8pCE46DF0ZJE73YR3aFvDAAdc=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/6WSCT74SQZBD3CUCXSSU3FK4QY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FbZ8pCE46DF0ZJE73YR3aFvDAAdc%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F6WSCT74SQZBD3CUCXSSU3FK4QY.jpg&h=c48c96b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■支聯會主席李卓人昨在銅鑼灣街站派揮春籌款。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】民主派多個主要政黨及組織，昨於銅鑼灣擺設街站派發揮春，為612人道支援基金籌款。民主派指在當前艱苦時勢下，港人更要團結加油，呼籲繼續捐款支持，協助被捕的2,000多名同路人。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：轟食環冚檔打壓  港人力撐支聯會 大坑狂掃自由花<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n余若薇親題「好人一生平安」<br />\n<br />\n民主黨、社民連、工黨、新民主同盟及支聯會昨午在銅鑼灣擺街站，派發10萬多份由公民黨創黨黨魁余若薇題字的「好人一生平安」揮春，上有基金的二維碼，方便市民捐款。街站亦設寫有「釋放所有政治犯」的橫額，歡迎市民在橫額上簽名，多名便衣警員期間到場監視，登記街站人士身份證。<br />\n<br />\n民主黨主席羅健熙指，港人在當前艱苦時勢下，更要團結加油，呼籲港人繼續捐款支持612基金，以協助被捕者獲得所需的援助。2019年以21歲之齡在荃灣區議會綠楊選區勝選、成為最年輕區議員的新民主同盟潘朗聰稱，香港在暴政打壓下，很多人面臨政治檢控，希望港人繼續支持612基金，他慨嘆：「『好人一生平安』喺呢個世界已非常之困難，我哋見到政府日日封區，搞到人心惶惶。」<br />\n<br />\n社民連主席黃浩銘表示，不少民主派人士都成為政權頭號打壓對象，包括再次被捕的網台主持傑斯、被拘押至今的「快必」譚得志和壹傳媒創辦人黎智英。他相信不少港人仍未死心，呼籲慷慨支持612基金，「我哋有呢個平台嘅時候，希望港人能透過呢個平台為手足打氣，唔好灰心、唔好喪志」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/xvPjJBDAlRtQ27aU9AdELtGR9-A=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/Y3JATPM745AQ3CPXD7LQEUA7MY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FxvPjJBDAlRtQ27aU9AdELtGR9-A%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FY3JATPM745AQ3CPXD7LQEUA7MY.jpg&h=fa81aeec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■泛民派發由余若薇親題的「好人一生平安」揮春，勉港人團結加油。"},{"pid":"09cf74a1b5fa79425218b124b2fb6aeb1bf796d7","tid":2399508,"uid":3241,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T08:19:42.000Z","msg":"多名便衣警員期間到場監視，登記街站人士身份證<br />\n<br />\n便咩撚衣<br />\n直接叫秘密警察/政治警察"},{"pid":"cbf698d3011e4d3d21c10b698773ee218f0e63b4","tid":2399508,"uid":91914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T08:23:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}